<figureCitation box="[408,495,330,357]" captionStart="FIGURES 57–62" captionStartId="14.[151,264,1947,1971]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,598,1917]" captionTargetId="figure-187@14.[151,1436,597,1924]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURES 57–62. Meria askhabadensis, ♂. 57. Habitus, dorsal view; 58. Head, frontal view; 59. Pronotum, dorsal view; 60. Pronotum, lateral view; 61. T3–T5, dorsal view; 62. T7, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6641342" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6641342/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="166">Fig. 57</figureCitation>
